Salomon Brothers Inc announced formationof global stock indexes designed to make it easy for portfoliomoney managers to invest all over the world.    "This is a way to put money into the Pacific or Europequickly," Laszlo Birinyi, Salomon vice president Laszlo Birinyitold a news conference.    The stock index products were developed in cooperation withthe Frank Russell Co, a pension fund consulting firm.    Birinyi said he would not be surprised if exchanges createfutures and options on the indexes. "Somebody will - If theydon't, we will," he said. Reuter&#3;